Arianne Zucker https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arianne_Zucker 0 Arianne Bethene Zuckerman (born June 3, 1974), credited professionally as Arianne Zucker, is an American actress and model. She is known for playing as Nicole Walker on the NBC daytime soap opera Days of Our Lives from 1998 to 2018.
